AI Content Generator

An interactive AI-powered content generation web application built using Streamlit and Large Language Models (LLMs).
The application allows users to generate high-quality content such as professional emails, LinkedIn posts, advertisements, and conversational text with support for multiple tones, languages, themes, and history tracking.
Features
User Authentication
-Secure login and signup system
-User-specific sessions
-Each userâ€™s data (history) is isolated

->AI Content Generation
-Powered by Meta LLaMA 3 (8B Instruct) via Hugging Face API
-Generate content based on:
-Content type
-Tone
-Language
-User-provided idea
-Supports professional, creative, formal, and friendly writing styles

->Dashboard
-Central workspace for managing AI-generated content
-Card-based UI inspired by modern dashboards
-Overview of features and workflow

->History Management
-Automatically saves every generated output
-Timestamped records
-View past drafts anytime
-Reload drafts back into the generator
-Copy saved content instantly

->Copy to Clipboard
-One-click copy button for generated text
-Useful for reuse across platforms

Theme Customization

->Multiple pastel themes:
-Lavender Pastel,Sky Blue,Rose Blush,Mint Green,Soft Yellow,Coffee Brown,Dark Mode support
Theme changes apply instantly

->Profile Management
-Upload profile picture
-Avatar displayed in sidebar
-Account creation date visible

->Settings
-Update account password securely

Help & User Guide
-Step-by-step instructions
-Usage tips
-Troubleshooting guide

->Tech Stack

Frontend & UI: Streamlit
Backend Logic: Python
AI Model: Meta LLaMA 3 (8B Instruct)
API Provider: Hugging Face Router
Authentication & Storage:
SQLite (users)
CSV files (history)
Styling: Custom CSS (Pastel themes + Dark mode)
